A service where Bitcoins can be bought and sold.

##You want to buy Bitcoins

* Cash (EUR) in the mail.  Mailed to a P.O. Box in Berlin, Germany 
* Cash, traded in-person in Berlin.
* SEPA (EUR), German bank transfer (EUR), international wire (you pay the fees)
* Western Union, Moneygram (receivable in EUR, you pay the fees)
* Condition: Customer sends first.

##You want to sell Bitcoins

Bitcoins may be sent to the exchange's bitcoin address (advance notification required) or to the exchange's e-mail address using [[Coinapult]].

* Cash (EUR) in the mail. Mailed with Expressbrief next-day deliver (only within Germany).
* Cash, traded in-person in Berlin.
* Mt. Gox redeemable code (EUR)(if available)
* SEPA (EUR), German bank transfer (EUR), international wire (you pay the fees)
* Western Union, Moneygram (I send EUROS, you pay the fees)
* Condition: Customer sends first.

##History

This service was first shared on June 19, 2012 (4.1).  The exchange is operated by the gold bullion merchant BitCoincommodities.com (4.2).

